definitions.definition: Any of various invertebrate animals , such as jellyfish , hydras , sea anemones , corals and formerly sponges and ctenophores that belong to the phylum Cnidaria .

main_definition: ( zoology ) Any of various invertebrate animals , such as jellyfish , hydras , sea anemones , corals and formerly sponges and ctenophores that belong to the phylum Cnidaria . [from 19th c.]
